	abstract = {Real-time {RT-PCR} has become a common technique, no longer 
limited to specialist core facilities. It is in many cases the only method for 
measuring {mRNA} levels of vivo low copy number targets of interest for which 
alternative assays either do not exist or lack the required sensitivity. 
