highly versatile microscopy platform, designated {VideoScan}, for the rapid and 
simultaneous analysis of various assay formats based on fluorescence microscopic 
detection. It uses standard commercial hardware components together with a 
modular in-house developed software package. Multiplex assays can be performed 
